# gen51 (C1): paraphrase-robust intent. The same intent is reached from many
# phrasings via keyword CUES + the self-model, not one rigid template. These
# phrasings are held out (not the exact ones in self.chat), so passing proves
# cue recognition, not enumerated strings.
> what is your name?
< I am parrot0.
> what should I call you?
< I am parrot0.
> tell me about yourself
< I am parrot0.
> what are you able to do?
< I can answer questions about facts and rules, do simple arithmetic, reason about cause and effect, compare quantities, tell whether two things are the same, remember things you tell me, read a short passage and pull out facts, track what a pronoun refers to, continue a sequence you teach me.
